author: El Laggron
description: Cogs made for the Discord server of Bronol, a Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Youtuber.
install_msg: Thanks for installing the repository! Please note that this isn't designed like a classic public cog, only made in mind of one specific server, but still made available to everyone. Support might not always be given, but you can still ask on the Cog Support server (Laggrons-Dumb-Cogs channel).
short: Cogs made for the Super Smash Bronol Discord server.
